  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F.",
    "Sauté minced garlic in olive oil over medium heat until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add avocado pulp to the skillet and cook for 2 minutes to warm.",
    "Pour in oat milk and lemon juice, season with salt and pepper, and simmer until thickened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Transfer mixture to a small baking dish and sprinkle grated parmesan evenly on top.",
    "Place dish in the oven and grill until cheese is golden and bubbly, 8-10 minutes.",
    "Remove from oven, let cool for 2 minutes, then garnish with chopped parsley.",
    "Serve hot as a silky, slightly bitter gratin."
  ],
